    <p align="left"><b style><span style="mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;">Obutumara
    okwikiriza Yesu Kristo nk&#146;Omujuni waitu, Omwoyo Arukwera aija okwikara
    omulitwe <font color="#1919AE">(Abarumi 8:9).</font><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">
    </span>Okwijura Omwoyo nikimanyisa okulekera Omwoyo Arukwera okulema,
    n&#146;okwebembera obwomeezi bwaitu.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>Baibuli
    nesoborra eti habwomeezi obwijwire Omwoyo Arukwera:
    </span></b> </p>
    <p align="center"><span style="
;
;
&gt;Baitu ebyana eby&#146;Omwoyo mbinu, okugonza, okusemererwa,
    Obusinge, okugumisiriza, oburungi, embabazi, okwesigwa, obucuteezi,
    okwerinda;&lt;span style=" mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>hali ebirukusisa
    biti busaho kiragiro <b><font color="#1919AE"><br>
    (Abagaratiya 5:22,23).</font></b></span> </p>
    <p align="left"><b><span style="
;;
&gt;Obutulekera Yesu
    okulema obwomeezi bwaitu, tugonza muno okusemeza Ruhanga, tuba n&#146;iroho
    ly&#146;okusoma Baibuli hamu nokusaba.&lt;span style=" mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>Tuba
    n&#146;okugonza okumanyisa abandi oburungi bwa Kristo, kandi tugonza okwikara
    n&#146;Abakristo abandi.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes"></span></b> </p>
